Did that, didn't complete.

Did it again, didn't complete again.

Force completed it, reappeared.

I'm stuck.

My log is found here: https://github.com/maculator/Crafts/blob/master/log

Well mods should be in the log but just in case:

- Kerbal Engineer

- Mechjeb2 (refuses to save custom windows but thats a different story...)

Aaand I got to admid I did some blackmagic and "injected" my R&D-Scenario in a fresh save shouldn't be a problem did that before...
